| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1009 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cea907d1-95ee-5cd9-9c4a-bbfdb57fc5d5"
